# Cara Kerja Scraping — End-to-End

---

## Siapa yang Memulai Scraping?

Ada **dua cara** scraping bisa dimulai:

| Cara | Trigger | Kapan |
|---|---|---|
| **Otomatis** | Celery Beat | Setiap hari jam 12.00 WIB |
| **Manual** | API `POST /api/v1/youtube/collect` | Kapan saja user trigger |

---

## Alur Otomatis (Celery Beat jam 12.00 WIB)

### Stage 1 — Fetch Trending Google Indonesia

**File:** `app/workers/youtube_worker.py` -> `fetch_trending_youtube_task`
**Service:** `app/services/youtube/pipeline_service.py` -> `fetch_and_store_trending()`

```
Celery Beat (jam 12:00 WIB)
  -> fetch_trending_youtube_task
  -> pytrends: ambil 10 topik trending Indonesia (geo=ID, period=24h)
  -> simpan ke tabel: trending_topics
  -> buat/update baris di tabel: keywords (1 keyword per trending topic)
  -> queue: collect_youtube_pipeline_task(keyword_id) per keyword baru
```

**Contoh data trending_topics yang tersimpan:**

| id | rank | title | traffic | geo | period |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| `23d09931-3a73-4a98-b23b-0a858f6f0e21` | 1 | gta | 200+ | ID | 24h |

---

### Stage 2 — Pipeline Per Keyword

**File:** `app/workers/youtube_worker.py` -> `collect_youtube_pipeline_task`

```
collect_youtube_pipeline_task(keyword_id)
  -> ambil Keyword dari tabel keywords
  -> INSERT ke tabel scrape_runs (status='running')  <- TANDA MULAI
  -> CollectorService -> YouTubeConnector
  -> EnsembleData API: GET /youtube/search/keyword?keyword=...&depth=2
      - Jika HTTP 495 (quota habis) -> fallback ke YouTube Data API v3
  -> normalize hasil -> INSERT ke tabel posts
  -> UPDATE scrape_runs (status='success'/'failed', video count, durasi)  <- TANDA SELESAI
  -> queue: collect_youtube_comments_task(post_id, keyword_id) per video baru
```

**Cara tahu berhasil atau tidak — cek tabel scrape_runs:**

Contoh baris nyata di DB server:

```
id:               750fc668-5504-4e6c-8bc0-5d65f9df7023
keyword_text:     ahok
status:           success           <- success / failed / fallback
api_source:       ensembledata      <- ensembledata / youtube_data_api
videos_fetched:   19
videos_new:       18
comments_fetched: 0
comments_new:     0
started_at:       2026-07-02 00:12:30 UTC
duration_seconds: 2.45
error_message:    (null)
```

**Nilai status:**
- `running`  — sedang berjalan sekarang
- `success`  — selesai normal
- `fallback` — selesai tapi ada error parsial
- `failed`   — gagal total

---

### Stage 3 — Komentar Per Video

**File:** `app/workers/youtube_worker.py` -> `collect_youtube_comments_task`

```
collect_youtube_comments_task(post_id, keyword_id, run_id)
  -> EnsembleData API: GET /youtube/comments?id=VIDEO_ID&cursor=...
  -> pagination via cursor sampai habis atau max_pages (5)
  -> INSERT ke tabel comments
  -> lexicon sentiment -> INSERT ke tabel lexicon_analyses
  -> UPDATE scrape_runs.comments_fetched + comments_new
```

