### 3. Langsung ke DB

```sql
-- Scraping terbaru
SELECT keyword_text, status, api_source, videos_new, comments_new, error_message, duration_seconds
FROM scrape_runs ORDER BY started_at DESC LIMIT 10;

-- Total post tersimpan
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM posts WHERE platform = 'youtube';
```

