## Peta Tabel yang Diisi

```
pytrends (Google Trends)
        |
        v
trending_topics      id, rank, title, traffic, geo, period
        |
        v
keywords             id, keyword, platform, is_active
        |
        v
scrape_runs          id, keyword_id, status, api_source, videos_*, comments_*, duration_seconds
        |
        |---> posts        id, external_id, keyword_id, platform, content, url, metadata (JSONB)
        |          |              metadata: views, likes, channel_id, channel_name, dll
        |          v
        |     comments     id, post_id, author, content, metadata
        |          |
        |          v
        |     lexicon_analyses   id, comment_id, sentiment, score
        |
        +---> scrape_runs  UPDATE: status=success, videos_new=N, comments_new=N
```

