## Alur Manual (via API)

```
POST /api/v1/youtube/collect
Body: { "keyword": "...", "keyword_id": "uuid", "max_pages": 2 }

-> langsung queue collect_youtube_pipeline_task(keyword_id)
-> alur sama mulai Stage 2
-> TIDAK ikut jadwal jam 12 WIB
```

---

## Fallback EnsembleData ke YouTube Data API

Jika EnsembleData respons HTTP 495 (quota habis):

```
Connector deteksi error 495
  -> gunakan YOUTUBE_DATA_API_KEY dari .env
  -> panggil YouTubeDataAPIClient.search_videos(keyword, max_results=50)
  -> scrape_run.api_source = 'youtube_data_api'
```

Fallback aktif untuk: search_by_keyword, search_by_hashtag, get_video_comments.
